---
import MainLayout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Stargazing with Binoculars - Observatory | The Astronomy Space"
  description="Complete guide to astronomy binoculars. Reviews, buying guides, observing techniques, and what you can see through binoculars from the Moon to deep sky objects."
>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="/images/Hero_choosing_binoculars.jpg" alt="Astronomy binoculars for stargazing" loading="eager" />
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/observatory/">Observatory</a></li>
          <li aria-current="page">Binoculars</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <h1>Stargazing with Binoculars</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Wide-field views of star clusters, nebulae, and the Milky Way — no setup required.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="intro-text">
        Binoculars are the most accessible way into astronomy. Grab them, step outside, and within seconds you're exploring the cosmos with both eyes — from sweeping Milky Way star fields to the moons of Jupiter. Our guides cover everything from choosing your first pair to mastering deep sky targets.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Articles Grid -->
  <section class="articles">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="articles-grid">

        <a href="/observatory/binoculars/choosing-first-binoculars/" class="article-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag tag-guide">Guide</span>
            <span class="card-time">12 min</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Choosing Your First Astronomy Binoculars</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Complete guide to specifications, magnifications, and features. Learn what 7x50, 10x50, and 15x70 mean and how to choose the right pair for your goals.</p>
          <span class="card-arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M7.5 5L12.5 10L7.5 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/observatory/binoculars/best-binoculars-2026/" class="article-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag tag-review">Review</span>
            <span class="card-time">18 min</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Best Binoculars for Astronomy in 2026</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Expert reviews and recommendations across all budgets. From affordable starter models under $100 to premium astronomical optics, with detailed comparisons.</p>
          <span class="card-arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M7.5 5L12.5 10L7.5 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/observatory/binoculars/beginners-guide/" class="article-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag tag-tutorial">Tutorial</span>
            <span class="card-time">10 min</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Beginner's Guide to Binocular Stargazing</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Start observing tonight. Essential techniques for holding binoculars steady, finding objects, and making the most of your first nights under the stars.</p>
          <span class="card-arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M7.5 5L12.5 10L7.5 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/observatory/binoculars/moon-observing/" class="article-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag tag-guide">Guide</span>
            <span class="card-time">15 min</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Observing the Moon with Binoculars</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Explore lunar craters, maria, and mountains in stunning detail. Month-by-month guide to lunar features and the best viewing times for each phase.</p>
          <span class="card-arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M7.5 5L12.5 10L7.5 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/observatory/binoculars/deep-sky-targets/" class="article-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag tag-guide">Guide</span>
            <span class="card-time">20 min</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Deep Sky Targets for Binoculars</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Essential nebulae, galaxies, and star clusters visible through binoculars. Seasonal sky tours with finding tips and what to expect for each target.</p>
          <span class="card-arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M7.5 5L12.5 10L7.5 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/observatory/binoculars/planetary-observing/" class="article-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag tag-guide">Guide</span>
            <span class="card-time">14 min</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Planetary Observing with Binoculars</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Track Venus, Mars, Jupiter, and Saturn throughout the year. Learn when to find planets, what details you can see, and how to distinguish them from stars.</p>
          <span class="card-arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M7.5 5L12.5 10L7.5 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/observatory/binoculars/accessories-maintenance/" class="article-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag tag-guide">Guide</span>
            <span class="card-time">8 min</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Binocular Accessories and Maintenance</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Essential accessories: tripod adapters, harnesses, red flashlights, and star charts. Plus care tips for cleaning, storage, and longevity.</p>
          <span class="card-arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M7.5 5L12.5 10L7.5 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/observatory/binoculars/image-stabilized/" class="article-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag tag-review">Review</span>
            <span class="card-time">12 min</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Image-Stabilized Binoculars for Astronomy</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">How image stabilization works, top models compared, and whether these premium binoculars are worth the investment for hand-held astronomical observing.</p>
          <span class="card-arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
              <path d="M7.5 5L12.5 10L7.5 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 50vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-image {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6) 50%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.92) 100%
    );
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Breadcrumbs */
  .breadcrumbs {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .breadcrumbs ol {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: '›';
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .breadcrumbs a {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
  }

  .breadcrumbs li[aria-current="page"] {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  /* Intro */
  .intro {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .intro-text {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Articles Grid */
  .articles {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .articles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .articles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Article Card */
  .article-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .article-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .article-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .article-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Card Meta Row */
  .card-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .card-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .tag-guide {
    background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15);
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
  }

  .tag-review {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    color: #60a5fa;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
  }

  .tag-tutorial {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
    color: #a78bfa;
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
  }

  .card-time {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* Card Content */
  .card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.35;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .article-card:hover .card-title {
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
  }

  .card-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }

  /* Arrow */
  .card-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    opacity: 0.4;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .card-arrow svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .article-card:hover .card-arrow {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(4px);
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
  }

  /* Container */
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
